/yarr (root folder)
    /frontend (React, Vue, etc., for the UI)
        /public (static files like images, icons)
        /src (JS, components, etc.)
        /assets (CSS, JS)
        package.json
    /backend (Express, Node.js, or other backend code)
        /controllers (handle business logic)
        /models (database schemas)
        /routes (API routes)
        /middlewares (authentication, file validation)
        package.json
    .gitignore
    README.md
